lines.text: [at the fiesta, Gene agrees to have his fortune told]
I see you do secret work for your country. You are what you call maybe - a federal agent.
Hey, this dame knows too much. Lets get out of here!
But now I see you go on another job - a much bigger one.
Soon - very soon. But you like this job very much. I see you riding through the night. You are happy. I think you are in love, senor.
Not that it's any of my business, Gene, but isn't it kind of dangerous leaving frog to guard him. That fellow is lible to get away.
[Gene, Smiley and the gang arrive in a Mexican town during a fiesta]
Gee, I betcha this celebration is for us!
I hardly think so. Besides, we gotta report to the Consul.
